name: Dino Delivery (itch) (Beanfox)
description:
----------------------------------------------

Parkour your way through 13 different levels getting harder and harder each time! 

Pick an Act as well as a Level and carry your chest toward the water. 

Your goal, to protect the chest from hitting the ground and make it to the water. Easy right?

----------------------------------------------

INCREDIBLY Easy Controls!

A - to move left

D - to move right

Space - to jump

----------------------------------------------
